flowchart TB
    Start([Start]) --> Enum[Enumerate scenes]
    Enum --> Load[Load scene]
    Load --> Res[Load sounds and textures]
    Res --> Input[Initialise input managers and action bindings]
    Input --> Wait[Wait for next frame]
    Unload --> Load
    Poll --> Unload[Unload scene and free resources]

subgraph Frame[Frame loop]
    Wait --> Poll[Apply events from input managers]
    Poll --> Update[Update entities]
    Update --> Render[Render scene]
    Render --> Wait
end
